'''Vuelta Ciclista Por Un Chile Lider''' was an elite men's professional [[road bicycle racing]] [[stage race]] held annually in [[Chile]]. The Vuelta Lider was created in 1997 by [[Líder|Lider]], the largest supermarket chain in Chile, and is sanctioned by the [[Chilean Cycling Federation]] (''Federación Ciclista de Chile''). The Vuelta Lider is the largest cycling race in Chile and serves as an important stop on the [[UCI America Tour]].
